message: Update build process to microbundle 0.6, move to `.mjs`, prepare for additional packages.
Add babel plugin (`htm/babel`) to precompile tagged templates to hyperscript or Virtual DOM objects.
temporary solution for committing dist files to github tagged releases
add a package.json for the preact integration to make module aliasing work
Bring in JSDOM in order to make the babel plugin actually work without a browser runtime
Babel: add tests for the babel plugin
Update tests to account for changing of package names
fix incorrect babel package name causing test failures
update microbundle, add optimized UMD and CJS builds
Update test harness and reorganize tests a bit.
Custom JSX parser and proper unit tests!
Reorganize build scripts into packages to fix htm/preact path
Add performance testing harness for use with d8
Add preact as peerDependency and bump devdep version
[mini] inline build to save a few more bytes
Update to Jest 24, move the JSX transform tests to ./test
Update to microbundle v0.10.0, enable mini builds
Update to microbundle v0.10.1, use the alias option to set MINI
Fix mini builds, add the .mjs file extension to module aliases
Add htm/react to package.json's files list

Remove peerDependencies to avoid warnings

It's not great, but we weren't going to be using them to limit version compat anyway.
Fixes #94.
Prepare README.md and package.json files for a new release
fix folks getting broken links by keeping mjs dist files around

Add typings for htm.bind(...)

The src/index.d.ts file is copied to dist/index.d.ts and
mini/index.d.ts as a part of the build process.
Prepare README.md and package.json files for v3 release
Fix typing file name & package.json field

Support node v13 with es modules

Creates conditional export that points "import" conditional exports to mjs files. This lets node load the esm version with having to set "type": "module" on the main package.json.

This is similar to the approach in the main preact repo - https://github.com/preactjs/preact/pull/2451
Add test for Node ESM conditional exports
Make export maps change non-breaking by exposing all files

Merge pull request #207 from developit/support-namespaces

[transform-jsx-to-htm] Add support for namespaces in JSX

Fix nodenext module support from TypeScript 4.7

* as per https://github.com/microsoft/TypeScript/issues/48235#issuecomment-1067363731
* follow-up https://github.com/preactjs/preact/pull/3513
